  <prompt>
    Create AiSummaryCarousel React component for displaying AI summaries of multiple uploaded documents
    with navigation, concurrent streaming, and per-document status tracking. Uses AiSummaryPanel for individual display.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    SPAARKE platform developer. Expert in React, TypeScript, Fluent UI v9, and PCF controls.
